final_hyps.green: The green object is the Goal that the agent must reach.
final_hyps.brown: Brown objects are False Walls. The agent can move through False Walls.
final_hyps.yellow: The yellow object is a Key. The agent can pick up the Key by moving into its space. While holding the Key, the agent is colored purple.
final_hyps.cyan: The cyan object is a KeyDoor. When the agent moves onto this object, the KeyDoor opens and the Key is destroyed. The agent cannot move through the KeyDoor while it is closed.

solve_plan: First determine that the green object is the Goal object. Since the agent is blocked by a cyan KeyDoor at (18, 8), it must first pick up the yellow Key at (13, 8) to unlock the KeyDoor. Move RIGHT 8 times to reach the Key. Pick up the Key and turn purple. Next, move LEFT 8 times back to the original x-position. Then, move DOWN 2 times to align with the y-axis of the KeyDoor (y=8). Move RIGHT 13 times to reach the KeyDoor at (18, 8) and unlock it. Finally, move DOWN 2 times and then RIGHT 1 time to reach the Goal object at (19, 10).
